        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "There is actually another one on similar lines #10071, which allows the TUI to connect to a headless nvim server. While not exactly same as attaching/detaching, it will allow us to connect similarly to tmux servers (which can be listed by, for example `tmux ls`).",
